{
  "doc_id": "CBE ANNUAL REPORT 2023-24",
  "text_blocks": [
    {
      "text": "PROFILE",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 52.4409,
        "y": 787.6698146484375,
        "w": 68.33400000000002,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "Â Has been serving Ethiopia since 1942.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 762.2185146484375,
        "w": 201.65879999999996,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "Â Pioneered ATM services in Ethiopia.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 744.9839146484375,
        "w": 190.13880000000003,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "Â Introduced Western Union Money Transfer Services to Ethiopia.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 727.7493146484375,
        "w": 327.5855999999999,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "Â Is the first Ethiopian bank to offer interest-free banking services.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 710.5146146484375,
        "w": 331.0763999999998,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "Â Has been playing a catalytic role in the socio-economic development of the nation.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 693.2800146484375,
        "w": 426.8592,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "Â Had 1,942 branches across the country as of 30 June 2024.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 676.0453146484375,
        "w": 303.46680000000003,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "Â Has strong correspondent relationships with about 38 renowned foreign banks and SWIFT bilateral key arrangements with over 750 banks.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 658.8107146484375,
        "w": 464.7083999999999,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "Â Achieved a strong asset position of Birr 1.4 trillion as of 30 June 2024.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 627.1761146484375,
        "w": 356.6136,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "Â Combines a wide capital base with above 48 thousand permanent and 33 thousand temporary employees.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 609.9414146484376,
        "w": 433.0283999999999,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "Â Is headquartered in a modern skyscraper (4B+G+48) that is the tallest in East Africa.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 578.3067146484375,
        "w": 430.0151999999997,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "VISION",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 52.4409,
        "y": 552.7155146484375,
        "w": 59.682000000000016,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "To become a world-class commercial bank financially driving Ethiopia's future.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 52.4409,
        "y": 526.3042146484374,
        "w": 389.6699999999999,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "MISSION",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 52.4409,
        "y": 501.6730146484375,
        "w": 72.19800000000001,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "We are committed to realizing stakeholders' values through enhanced financial intermediation globally, deploying highly motivated and skilled employees.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 52.4409,
        "y": 475.26171464843753,
        "w": 472.10999999999996,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "MOTTO",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 52.4409,
        "y": 436.2305146484375,
        "w": 56.168000000000006,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "The Bank You Can Always Rely on!",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 52.4409,
        "y": 409.81921464843754,
        "w": 167.89079999999993,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "VALUES",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 52.4409,
        "y": 376.6461146484375,
        "w": 61.348,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "i) Integrity",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 52.4409,
        "y": 350.23491464843755,
        "w": 56.18279999999997,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We are committed to the highest ideals of honor and integrity.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 329.7083146484375,
        "w": 326.7684,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We are committed to acting in an honest and trustworthy manner.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 312.47361464843743,
        "w": 343.9403999999999,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We are committed to firmly adhering to ethical principles and standards.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 295.23901464843743,
        "w": 374.36039999999974,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "ii) Service Excellence",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 52.4409,
        "y": 272.79231464843747,
        "w": 109.70280000000008,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We are committed to maintaining the highest operating standards.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 252.26571464843755,
        "w": 347.1443999999999,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We are committed to being a preferred brand in service quality in the minds of customers and the general public.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 235.03111464843755,
        "w": 483.1151999999997,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We strive to build long lasting relationships with our customers.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 203.39641464843749,
        "w": 330.5243999999999,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "iii) Professionalism",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 52.4409,
        "y": 180.9498146484375,
        "w": 100.7268,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We take ownership and personal responsibility for all what we do.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 160.42321464843758,
        "w": 340.3403999999999,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We are professionals in conduct and treat customers with the utmost respect.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 143.18861464843758,
        "w": 398.7443999999997,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We are responsive to the needs and interests of our customers.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 125.95391464843749,
        "w": 325.50960000000003,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We maintain the confidentiality and privacy of all customers.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 108.71931464843749,
        "w": 314.9123999999998,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We continually develop ourselves to maintain leading-edge capabilities.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 91.48461464843751,
        "w": 372.0671999999998,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We apply our knowledge and competence to our competitive advantage.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 74.25001464843751,
        "w": 378.94439999999975,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "ii",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 36.0534,
        "y": 31.686414648437562,
        "w": 5.616,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "VALUES - (Continued)",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 52.4409,
        "y": 787.6698146484375,
        "w": 172.75999999999996,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Iv) Empowerment",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 52.4409,
        "y": 761.1352146484375,
        "w": 94.57080000000005,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We distinguish employees as valuable organizational resources.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 738.3309146484376,
        "w": 329.82959999999997,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We promote delegation of duties and responsibilities.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 717.4012146484375,
        "w": 280.6295999999999,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We maintain an atmosphere that inspires confidence and take ownership.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 696.4715146484375,
        "w": 380.21639999999985,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We take responsibility, support each other and serve customers in a courteous and respectful manner.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 675.5418146484375,
        "w": 479.6459999999997,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We recognize our employees for their best achievements.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 637.9344146484375,
        "w": 299.0495999999998,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "V) Innovative Organization",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 52.441,
        "y": 611.7927146484375,
        "w": 143.96280000000004,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We go above and beyond to find solutions to stakeholder problems leveraging technology where possible.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 588.9884146484375,
        "w": 467.45519999999993,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We anticipate and respond to internal and external changes through constant improvement and adjustment.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 551.3810146484375,
        "w": 474.8712,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We establish a culture that nurtures individual and group learning.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 513.7736146484375,
        "w": 344.2524,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We retain and disseminate tacit knowledge across the Bank.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 492.84391464843753,
        "w": 311.75759999999997,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Vi) Teamwork",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 52.441,
        "y": 466.7022146484375,
        "w": 71.56800000000003,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We respect one another and cooperate in our work.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 443.8979146484375,
        "w": 270.24959999999993,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We recognize the importance of teamwork for our success.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 422.96821464843754,
        "w": 305.34959999999995,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We collaborate and support one another to ensure process integration and minimize external business challenges.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 402.0385146484375,
        "w": 481.33919999999983,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Vii) Respect for Diversity",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 52.441,
        "y": 359.21911464843754,
        "w": 130.59360000000007,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We are responsive to cultural, ethical, religious or other values of employees and customers.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 336.4148146484375,
        "w": 469.3271999999999,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We value diversity of ideas and viewpoints of our employees.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 315.4851146484375,
        "w": 316.72439999999995,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We foster an environment of inclusiveness, where all people, regardless of their sex, age, belief, etc. can exercise their maximum potential.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 294.5554146484376,
        "w": 453.9179999999997,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We are committed to address the needs of our customers, regardless of their sex, age, education etc.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 256.9480146484375,
        "w": 440.8391999999999,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We are committed to listening to one another and respond appropriately.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 219.34051464843753,
        "w": 379.53239999999977,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Viii) Corporate Citizenship",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 52.441,
        "y": 193.1989146484375,
        "w": 139.3548,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We value the importance of our role in national development endeavours and stand up for this commitment.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 170.39461464843748,
        "w": 467.2499999999997,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We abide by the laws of Ethiopia and other countries in which we do business.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 132.78711464843752,
        "w": 402.6431999999999,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We care about the society's welfare and the environment.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 111.8574146484375,
        "w": 299.4096,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Â We believe that the sustainability of our business depends on our ability to maintain and build public confidence.",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 60.9449,
        "y": 90.92781464843756,
        "w": 456.8579999999999,
        "h": 0.0
      },
      "page_number": 5
    },
